channel.title: Models in Graphics section
channel.description: You all do understand, that moving models to the Graphics section here, is like inviting moparscapers over here. And even the most intelligent moparscapers, are still retards. So I think you all should stop doing that, to preserve the average iq of the members of this board. Already I've seen retards posting stupid moparscape shit in that board, and it's cluttering up the board.

item.title: Models in Graphics section
item.dc:creator: @sanga282 sanga282
item.description:
@sanga282 wrote:

[quote=“Moparisthebest, post:39, topic:295452”][quote author=sanga282 link=topic=391455.msg2933056#msg2933056 date=1251398396]

Why would models from there get moved over here anyway? Isn’t that what the model section over there is for?

yeah but they dont accept high poly models and the moparscapers are progressing through model programs to things like 3DS or C4D and they are posting things too HQ for the RS client
[/quote]

So if they want to post high poly models, mods could tell them to cut down the count and repost them, who says they should be moved over here? On the other hand, if they want to post them over here then that is fine.[/quote]
the reason the mods over there think they should be moved is because that models section is for models that go into a client and those models wont because of their texture quality, detail, poly count etc so they then move them here

Read full topic
